Package mystars.forms.cgui

Class ConsoleGraphicUserInterface

  • java.lang.Object
    • mystars.forms.cgui.ConsoleGraphicUserInterface
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    IUserInterface
    public class ConsoleGraphicUserInterface
extends java.lang.Object
implements IUserInterface
    This class creates the respective form objects and manages the graphical user interfaces for the console that users will use.
